                job_id,
                auto_job_schedule_name,
                auto_job_action_name,
                server_name,
                smb_user_name,
                smb_password,
                smb_folder,
                local_folder,
                last_stats,
                start_date,
                end_date,
                fatal_errors,
                warnings,
                last_updated,
                init_hash
            ) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
